post.description: Returns a quote for a given security.

GetQuoteOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetQuoteResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetQuoteResult>
    <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
    <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
    <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
    <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
    <tns:SourceAPI>string</tns:SourceAPI>
    <tns:InstrumentType>string</tns:InstrumentType>
    <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
    <tns:Identifier>string</tns:Identifier>
    <tns:IdentifierType>string</tns:IdentifierType>
    <tns:Market>string</tns:Market>
    <tns:MarketIdentificationCode>string</tns:MarketIdentificationCode>
    <tns:DateTime>string</tns:DateTime>
    <tns:UTCOffset><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:UTCOffset>
    <tns:Currency>string</tns:Currency>
    <tns:Open><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Open>
    <tns:High><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:High>
    <tns:Low><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Low>
    <tns:Last><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Last>
    <tns:LastSize><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:LastSize>
    <tns:Volume><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Volume>
    <tns:VolumeDate>string</tns:VolumeDate>
    <tns:PreviousClose><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PreviousClose>
    <tns:PreviousCloseDate>string</tns:PreviousCloseDate>
    <tns:Change><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Change>
    <tns:PercentChange><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:PercentChange>
    <tns:ExtendedHoursType>string</tns:ExtendedHoursType>
    <tns:ExtendedHoursDateTime>string</tns:ExtendedHoursDateTime>
    <tns:ExtendedHoursPrice><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:ExtendedHoursPrice>
    <tns:ExtendedHoursChange><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:ExtendedHoursChange>
    <tns:ExtendedHoursPercentChange><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:ExtendedHoursPercentChange>
    <tns:Bid><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Bid>
    <tns:BidSize><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:BidSize>
    <tns:BidDateTime>string</tns:BidDateTime>
    <tns:Ask><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Ask>
    <tns:AskSize><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:AskSize>
    <tns:AskDateTime>string</tns:AskDateTime>
    <tns:TradingHalted><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:TradingHalted>
   </tns:GetQuoteResult>
  </tns:GetQuoteResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

GetChartBarsInput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Header>
  <wsse:Security xmlns:wsse="http://docs.oasis-open.org/wss/2004/01/oasis-200401-wss-wssecurity-secext-1.0.xsd" xmlns:wsu="http://docs.oasis-open.org/wss/2004/01/oasis-200401-wss-wssecurity-utility-1.0.xsd">
   <wsse:UsernameToken>
    <wsse:Username>string</wsse:Username>
    <wsse:Password>string</wsse:Password>
    <wsse:Nonce EncodingType="string">string</wsse:Nonce>
    <wsu:Created>string</wsu:Created>
   </wsse:UsernameToken>
   <wsu:Timestamp wsu:Id="string">
    <wsu:Created>string</wsu:Created>
    <wsu:Expires>string</wsu:Expires>
   </wsu:Timestamp>
  </wsse:Security>
  <tns:Header xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:Username>string</tns:Username>
   <tns:Password>string</tns:Password>
   <tns:Tracer>string</tns:Tracer>
  </tns:Header>
 </soapenv:Header>
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetChartBars xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/"><!-- mandatory -->
   <tns:Identifier>string</tns:Identifier>
   <tns:IdentifierType><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:IdentifierType>
   <tns:StartTime>string</tns:StartTime>
   <tns:EndTime>string</tns:EndTime>
   <tns:Precision>string</tns:Precision>
   <tns:Period><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Period>
   <tns:AdjustmentMethod>string</tns:AdjustmentMethod>
   <tns:IncludeExtended><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:IncludeExtended>
  </tns:GetChartBars>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

GetChartBarsOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:GetChartBarsResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:GetChartBarsResult>
    <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
    <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
    <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
    <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
    <tns:Security>
     <tns:CIK>string</tns:CIK>
     <tns:CUSIP>string</tns:CUSIP>
     <tns:Symbol>string</tns:Symbol>
     <tns:ISIN>string</tns:ISIN>
     <tns:Valoren>string</tns:Valoren>
     <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
     <tns:Market>string</tns:Market>
     <tns:MarketIdentificationCode>string</tns:MarketIdentificationCode>
     <tns:MostLiquidExchange><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:MostLiquidExchange>
     <tns:CategoryOrIndustry>string</tns:CategoryOrIndustry>
    </tns:Security>
    <tns:Timing>string</tns:Timing>
    <tns:SourceAPI>string</tns:SourceAPI>
    <tns:InstrumentType>string</tns:InstrumentType>
    <tns:ChartBars>
     <tns:ChartBar><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
      <tns:StartDateTime>string</tns:StartDateTime>
      <tns:EndDateTime>string</tns:EndDateTime>
      <tns:UTCOffset><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:UTCOffset>
      <tns:Open><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Open>
      <tns:High><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:High>
      <tns:Low><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Low>
      <tns:Close><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Close>
      <tns:Volume><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Volume>
      <tns:Trades><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Trades>
      <tns:TWAP><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:TWAP>
      <tns:VWAP><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:VWAP>
      <tns:Currency>string</tns:Currency>
      <tns:Session>string</tns:Session>
      <tns:AdjustmentRatio><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:AdjustmentRatio>
     </tns:ChartBar>
    </tns:ChartBars>
   </tns:GetChartBarsResult>
  </tns:GetChartBarsResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
